name: Bird Of Fire
description: In mythology the Phoenix symbolises the cycle of birth and death, transformation, uprising and renewal. For me this design expresses perfectly my feelings about the state of the world today. The feeing that the old world, the old story that we have co-created is burning and dying and the hope that, with courage and imagination, from the ashes something new and far better will emerge. (3000 x 3900 px. All purchases for personal use only).
